s increased, while the human being in sports was and still is very often exploited or mistreated. These problems often relate to the political dimension as well. Consequently, it seems very promising and necessary alike to take a closer look at the interrelation of sports and politics. The present volume addresses this interrelation from different angles, when talking about issues like racism, gender inequality, or classism.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aHomophobia in sports. 0aRacism in sports. 0aSportsxMoral and ethical aspects. 0aSportsxPolitical aspects.1 aAiello, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBachynski, Kathleen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCollura, Francesco, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHeenan, Tom, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHirschfelder, Nicole, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJacob, Frank, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJacob, Frank, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMarston, Steve, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRiess, Steven A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package English 2020z978311069628808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDe Gruyter English eBooks 2020 - UCz978311065906108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020 Englishz978311070471608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of e